olloid-based materials are discussed. To the best of\nthe authors knowledge, such a detailed study of the refractive index associated\nwith erbium impurities in silica is being reported for the first time in the\nliterature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2021 20:25:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-28"}
