py value was lower, due to the uniformity of intensities\nin these areas. To complete this study, it was performed a data analysis with\nthe set of intensities in each area. This allowed to distinguish between the\nareas of interest according to the value of the intensities, having a value\ngreater than 3 {\\sigma}. Finally, it is shown a technique to visually highlight\nthe malignant tumor and/or microcalcification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2021 21:24:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 22:11:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-03"}
