es several pain points that could improve the\neffectiveness of future machine learning based code generation/retrieval\ndeveloper assistants, and demonstrates when developers prefer code generation\nover code retrieval and vice versa. We release all data and software to pave\nthe road for future empirical studies and development of better models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2021 01:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 02:07:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Sep 2021 08:49:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-23"}
