ocity). The nature of the Lifshitz\ntransition and the scaling behaviour (both) at the critical coupling strength\nis different in the two cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2021 07:42:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2021 18:25:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-11"}
