ageNet with\ntopology learnable and achieve a top-1 error rate of 23.8% in 2.1 GPU-day.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2021 12:16:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-28"}
